title: Jenny Wilson - Hardships! [2009] [Album] MP3 / 192 / CD
description:
The new Jenny Wilson album "Hardships!" is confirmed for release on February 25 via her own new label Gold Medal Recordings.

"Hardships! is a collection of 13 modern work songs for all times. It contains shimmering in-preparedness-poetry and raw r'n'b, in a way you've never heard it before. I want Hardships! to feel simple as salt and pepper on your tongue. And sparkling as a burning matchstick that you can burn on your fingertips on!"

Watch out for the knock-out single "The Wooden Chair."
